title: Executive Order 5039-General Joe Wheeler Dam
content: It is hereby directed that the Dam proposed in the report to Congress, House Document 1262-64th Congress, First Sesssion, and referred to therein as Dam No. 3, be named General Joe Wheeler Dam.
citation: Calvin Coolidge, Executive Order 5039-General Joe Wheeler Dam Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/360759
